  <Dialog id="3" name="MSG_003_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0000"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 110 0 -1 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 6 0 0}Today... I'm moving far away.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="4" name="MSG_004_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0000"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 110 0 -1 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 7 0 0}Um... Dad told me I would always be his daughter.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
    <Page spk="0000"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 110 0 -1 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 8 0 0}No matter how far away, we're still family...[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
    <Page spk="0000"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 110 0 -1 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 9 0 0}So I don't have to be sad![n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="5" name="MSG_004_5_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0000"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 110 0 -1 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 10 0 0}Family is special...[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
    <Page spk="0000"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 110 0 -1 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 11 0 0}Do you think I'll have a family of my own one day?[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="6" name="SEL_005_0_0" type="Selection">
    <Option><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}I'm sure you will.]]></Option>
    <Option><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}No idea.]]></Option>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="7" name="MSG_006_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0000"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 110 0 -1 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 12 0 0}{f 5 13 13 15 110}Yeah, you're right! I hope...[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="8" name="MSG_007_0_0" type="Message">
